<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://bootgod.dyndns.org:7777/profile.php?id=4038">http://bootgod.dyndns.org:7777/profile.php?id=4038</a><!-- m -->
<br />
<br />So, on this PCB there are 2x 74HC161, 74HC32, 74HC00 and 74HC245 chips. So, there is an extra 74HC245 chip, so, anybody know, how to connect this chip???

		

